Package toxi.color

Class NamedColor

java.lang.Object
toxi.color.NamedColor
public class NamedColor extends Object
Defines a list of named colors across the spectrum and provides a means to access them by name (strings) dynamically (e.g. using config files or when building ColorThemes)
